items.sentence: Tom said he didn\'t really care what happened.
Tom said he doesn\'t know how to speak French.
Tom was ticketed for passing on a yellow line.
Tom doesn\'t like the way Mary treats her dog.
Tom doesn\'t like working on an empty stomach.
Tom doesn\'t look like the man in the picture.
Tom doesn\'t need to get up so early tomorrow.
Tom doesn\'t need to know where Mary is going.
Tom doesn\'t need to know who gave this to us.
Tom said he had been asked a lot of questions.
